snippet.title: iPhone Amber Alert ~ How To Turn On Or Off
snippet.description:
Do you know that your iPhone has an Amber Alert setting and also a government emergency alert setting?  You can configure your iPhone to receive these notifications or to turn them off. 

In this video, I will show you how to turn the amber alert on or off for your iPhone. My cell service and iPhone 5 are with Verizon.

A lot of people do not want government notification alerts coming to their phones all hours of the day.
